description:
Melotte 15 - The Heart Of The Heart

Equipment
Williamoptics RedCat 51
Celestronuniverse Edge HD 8” w/Hyperstar
Zwoasi 1600mm x2, 224MC, 30mm Guide Scope, ASIAIR, ASIAIR PRO, & EAF
Baaderplanetarium F2 HA, OIII, & SII, Astronomik HA, OIII, & SII Filters
Skywatcherusa EQ6-R Mount

Acquisition
-SII - 407x90” (10.8hrs) Hyperstar & 177x180” (8.85hrs) RedCat 10/27 - 18.67hrs total
-HA - 388x90” (9.7hrs) Hyperstar & 152x180” (7.6hrs) RedCat 11/4 - 17.3hrs total
-OIII - 410x90” (10.25hrs) Hyperstar & 155x180” (7.75hrs) Redcat 10/20 - 18hrs total
-53.97hrs Total Integration Time
-50 Darks, 50 Flats, 250 Bias per session
-Gain 139
-Temp-15c
-Bortle 5

@itz_reg was gracious enough to give me his data to add to my stack:
SII - 13.41hrs 
HA - 22.95hrs
OIII - 9.90hrs
- 46.26 Total integration Time

This stack has a total integration time of 100.23hrs!
